(719, 'TPP - Global Attributes on Add-to-Cart Tab', 'GLOBAL_ATTRIBUTES_ON_ATC_TAB', '0', 'Set this to 1 if you want the Attributes to appear on the Add-To-Cart tab. They will only show up if the product has attributes to show. YOU MUST ALSO LEAVE THE Global Attributes on Tab OPTION ENABLED. This will override the standalone tab and show the attributes on the Add-To-Cart tab only. If the Add-To-Cart tab is set to false, this will be ignored and the attributes will follow their own tab settings.', 46, 5, '2008-12-05 12:06:19', '2007-01-12 22:07:11', NULL, 'zen_cfg_select_option(array(\'0\', \'1\'),'),
